14
00:01:31,500 --> 00:01:35,300
= Princess Agents =

15
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:37,940
= Episode 28 =

16
00:02:17,130 --> 00:02:18,720
Take the corpses. Let’s go!

17
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:19,670
- Aye.
- Aye.

18
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:26,260
Yuwen Huai’s men?

19
00:02:27,050 --> 00:02:27,570
Yes.

20
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,170
Our people

21
00:02:29,170 --> 00:02:30,600
heard this from your brother.

22
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,240
They never made it to the Oriole Courtyard

23
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,490
and were killed.

24
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,160
Looks like

25
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,530
there is no need to alert Princess.

26
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:38,310
She has nothing to worry about.

27
00:02:39,380 --> 00:02:41,450
Yuwen Yue isn’t
as cold-hearted as he seems.

28
00:02:41,820 --> 00:02:43,970
He betrayed Yan Xun.

29
00:02:44,350 --> 00:02:46,090
But actually, he cares a lot about him.

30
00:02:48,950 --> 00:02:51,680
Good. At lease, someone can do

31
00:02:52,010 --> 00:02:53,460
what I can’t.

32
00:02:54,780 --> 00:02:56,000
I hope

33
00:02:56,410 --> 00:02:57,900
he is braver than me.

34
00:02:58,270 --> 00:02:58,990
Young Master.

35
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,040
You may leave.

36
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:02,310
Aye.

37
00:03:06,420 --> 00:03:09,140
= Oriole Courtyard =

38
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:16,640
Your Excellency.

39
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,230
Has the water been tested?

40
00:03:18,370 --> 00:03:19,380
Didn’t we test the water

41
00:03:19,380 --> 00:03:20,730
from the well yesterday?

42
00:03:57,340 --> 00:03:58,240
From now on, all meals

43
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,300
must be tested.

44
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:01,260
I will get some mice.

45
00:04:01,690 --> 00:04:02,910
After the mice eat the food,

46
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:04,100
don’t start eating immediately.

47
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:06,570
Some poison takes effect
more quickly than others.

48
00:04:06,570 --> 00:04:08,690
Some are slow in taking effect.

49
00:04:09,550 --> 00:04:11,430
We need to wait for at least two days.

50
00:04:11,430 --> 00:04:12,860
If the mice are fine,

51
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:14,350
we can eat the food then.

52
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:15,780
The same goes for water.

53
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:17,780
It’s scorching.

54
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:19,370
The food will go bad in two days.

55
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:24,240
Bad food is still better than poison.

56
00:04:26,860 --> 00:04:28,700
= Weipin Pavilion =

57
00:04:28,700 --> 00:04:29,550
His Excellency Yan

58
00:04:29,550 --> 00:04:30,910
is safe for now.

59
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:33,360
Your job is done.

60
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,660
The four of you can go back

61
00:04:34,660 --> 00:04:36,230
to Yanbei and find Mr. Wu.

62
00:04:36,410 --> 00:04:37,560
I can also

63
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,800
give you some money

64
00:04:40,130 --> 00:04:41,500
or help you

65
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:42,220
start a business.

66
00:04:42,810 --> 00:04:44,080
The four of you are quite smart.

67
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,270
You can make a living out of this.

68
00:04:49,770 --> 00:04:51,440
We don’t want that.

69
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,480
We’d like to follow you.

70
00:04:52,710 --> 00:04:53,880
Are you sure?

71
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:56,950
If not, we wouldn’t have

72
00:04:56,950 --> 00:04:57,870
invited you over.

73
00:04:58,450 --> 00:04:59,270
If you choose to follow me,

74
00:05:00,290 --> 00:05:01,750
every day ahead of you

75
00:05:02,430 --> 00:05:04,320
is more dangerous than before.

76
00:05:04,870 --> 00:05:05,650
I know.

77
00:05:06,910 --> 00:05:08,140
We are all from Yanbei.

78
00:05:09,620 --> 00:05:11,440
When Yanbei was in danger,

79
00:05:12,050 --> 00:05:13,690
all our family members were killed.

80
00:05:14,340 --> 00:05:15,870
We are homeless.

81
00:05:17,190 --> 00:05:19,950
We’ve been working for you

82
00:05:20,310 --> 00:05:21,360
just so we can avenge their deaths

83
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,490
someday.

84
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,060
So

85
00:05:26,180 --> 00:05:27,420
you’d like to join me?

86
00:05:28,210 --> 00:05:28,950
Yes. Join you

87
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:30,280
and His Excellency.

88
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:31,760
I’m sure

89
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:33,000
after what His Excellency went through,

90
00:05:33,190 --> 00:05:34,580
he’ll get back on his feet.

91
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:37,510
All our enemies

92
00:05:38,140 --> 00:05:39,410
are in Chang’an.

93
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,440
Aren’t you afraid

94
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,620
of being killed?

95
00:05:46,690 --> 00:05:47,590
If it is for Yanbei,

96
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:48,860
we are glad

97
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:50,040
to take that risk.

98
00:05:50,950 --> 00:05:51,810
Besides,

99
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,930
who knows what will happen?

100
00:05:54,620 --> 00:05:57,190
Maybe once we kill the Emperor of Wei,

101
00:05:57,790 --> 00:05:58,820
His Excellency will reward

102
00:05:58,820 --> 00:05:59,650
us with posts in Yanbei.

103
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,040
Zhong Yu,

104
00:06:03,420 --> 00:06:04,680
please take us.

105
00:06:05,090 --> 00:06:06,230
We will try our best

106
00:06:06,230 --> 00:06:07,530
to learn.

107
00:06:07,530 --> 00:06:09,260
We won’t be a burden on you.

108
00:06:15,530 --> 00:06:17,170
I am not sure if I am helping you

109
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,360
or putting you in danger.

110
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,170
Is that a yes?

111
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:29,060
Since our lives are on the line,

112
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,600
we must hone our skills.

113
00:06:32,590 --> 00:06:34,040
If you want to stay,

114
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,780
you must obey my orders.

115
00:06:36,460 --> 00:06:38,210
Otherwise, you’ll die in vain.

116
00:06:38,540 --> 00:06:40,670
Yes, we’ll be obedient!

117
00:06:40,670 --> 00:06:41,310
We will!

118
00:06:41,310 --> 00:06:42,660
Me too!

119
00:06:44,950 --> 00:06:46,210
You are all here.

120
00:06:46,460 --> 00:06:47,910
Then you must’ve heard

121
00:06:47,910 --> 00:06:49,110
everything we said.

122
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,530
From now on,

123
00:06:53,130 --> 00:06:54,300
we live and die together.

124
00:06:55,490 --> 00:06:56,490
- Yes!
- Yes!

125
00:07:39,060 --> 00:07:41,540
= Pine Hall =

126
00:08:28,190 --> 00:08:29,160
Your Excellency Yan Xun.

127
00:08:29,470 --> 00:08:30,250
No weapon is allowed

128
00:08:30,250 --> 00:08:31,410
at the Oriole Courtyard.

129
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:33,510
Any violation will be a felony.

130
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:34,750
We are just doing our job.

131
00:08:34,910 --> 00:08:36,500
Please try to understand it.

132
00:08:59,980 --> 00:09:01,500
Thank you for your cooperation

133
00:09:08,340 --> 00:09:09,060
We are good.

134
00:09:25,980 --> 00:09:26,780
Will anyone else

135
00:09:26,780 --> 00:09:27,980
come tonight?

136
00:09:29,300 --> 00:09:31,700
I don’t know. Sleep first.

137
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:34,670
Don’t forget to wake me up.

138
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,040
My lady,

139
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:51,450
only one of them

140
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,400
that went to test Chu Qiao came back.

141
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:57,560
He said Yan Xun’s maid

142
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,370
is skilled and merciless.

143
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,410
But her skills

144
00:10:01,410 --> 00:10:03,300
are of Yuwen’s style

145
00:10:03,430 --> 00:10:05,540
instead of that of the underworld.

146
00:10:06,940 --> 00:10:08,950
Her skills are from the Yuwen family?

147
00:10:09,490 --> 00:10:11,830
Shall we test her again?

148
00:10:13,510 --> 00:10:14,450
No need.

149
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:22,760
Your Excellency Yan Xun.

150
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:25,940
It’s been a while. You’re good as usual.

151
00:10:26,620 --> 00:10:28,550
Tell me if you need anything.

152
00:10:29,610 --> 00:10:31,210
And this is...

153
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:32,520
My maid.

154
00:10:33,430 --> 00:10:34,410
Only one maid?

155
00:10:34,700 --> 00:10:35,830
There’s another one.

156
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:38,180
Her face was scratched yesterday

157
00:10:38,180 --> 00:10:39,570
by assassins.

158
00:10:39,940 --> 00:10:41,300
She is resting inside now.

159
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,040
Chang’an

160
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:44,340
is becoming less and less safe.

161
00:10:44,610 --> 00:10:46,230
I’ll ask the government

162
00:10:46,230 --> 00:10:47,950
to get to the bottom of it.

163
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:49,230
Don’t worry.

164
00:10:49,610 --> 00:10:50,290
No need.

165
00:10:51,180 --> 00:10:52,410
I killed them all.

166
00:10:52,410 --> 00:10:54,180
You’re highly skilled.

167
00:10:54,350 --> 00:10:55,890
Of course you aren’t afraid of them.

168
00:10:57,830 --> 00:10:59,740
You know this gentleman, don’t you?

169
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,470
The second son of the Wei family.

170
00:11:02,410 --> 00:11:03,820
We’re old friends.

171
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,810
What are you doing here?

172
00:11:07,660 --> 00:11:09,050
My guards said

173
00:11:09,050 --> 00:11:11,020
you hid weapons in this yard.

174
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:13,430
I came here to have a check.

175
00:11:13,930 --> 00:11:15,030
Check?

176
00:11:15,190 --> 00:11:17,490
What? Is there a problem?

177
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:19,970
When we came here,

178
00:11:19,970 --> 00:11:21,160
we were already checked.

179
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,670
Can’t we

180
00:11:22,670 --> 00:11:24,220
check you again?

181
00:11:24,830 --> 00:11:26,280
I’m not sure if the previous check

182
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:27,290
is thorough enough.

183
00:11:27,290 --> 00:11:29,010
So I’m doing it myself.

184
00:11:35,180 --> 00:11:35,810
Search!

185
00:11:37,350 --> 00:11:38,020
Wait!

186
00:11:40,570 --> 00:11:41,950
That’s loud.

187
00:11:41,950 --> 00:11:43,390
Did you raise your voice to me?

188
00:11:43,850 --> 00:11:44,870
You really think

189
00:11:44,870 --> 00:11:46,550
you’re still that hoity-toity Yan Xun?

190
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:49,730
Let me make it clear.

191
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:51,760
His Majesty spared you.

192
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:54,280
But I won’t tolerate violators
of the rules.

193
00:11:58,150 --> 00:11:59,020
Your Excellency.

194
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:01,460
Let them search.

195
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:04,450
We are on the chopping block.

196
00:12:05,770 --> 00:12:06,960
We can’t battle them.

197
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:09,810
Your maid

198
00:12:09,810 --> 00:12:11,330
seems like a clever girl.

199
00:12:11,790 --> 00:12:13,620
Your Excellency, be smart

200
00:12:13,950 --> 00:12:15,170
and suffer less.

201
00:12:19,890 --> 00:12:20,630
Search!

202
00:12:30,990 --> 00:12:31,750
That way!

203
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:32,330
Aye.

204
00:12:33,290 --> 00:12:33,840
This way!

205
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,660
Aye.

206
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:42,700
Move!

207
00:13:17,470 --> 00:13:19,190
What happened to this maid?

208
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,240
You’ll know

209
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,130
if you’re

210
00:13:29,630 --> 00:13:31,290
disfigured.

211
00:13:35,620 --> 00:13:37,790
Young Master, nothing suspicious.

212
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,700
If not,

213
00:13:40,250 --> 00:13:42,830
please show yourselves out.

214
00:13:42,830 --> 00:13:45,790
Wait, we haven’t checked the wound yet.

215
00:13:49,910 --> 00:13:50,890
Young Master Wei,

216
00:13:50,890 --> 00:13:52,150
isn’t that necessary?

217
00:13:53,450 --> 00:13:56,320
That is up to me.

218
00:13:58,800 --> 00:14:00,440
His Excellency’s maid

219
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,850
isn’t for anyone to see.

220
00:14:03,390 --> 00:14:04,540
His Excellency?

221
00:14:05,770 --> 00:14:07,290
Marquis Dingbei

222
00:14:07,290 --> 00:14:08,380
has been beheaded.

223
00:14:08,710 --> 00:14:10,440
What kind of Excellency is he?

224
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,430
Wei Shuyou,

225
00:14:15,470 --> 00:14:16,970
you’ve way over the line!

226
00:14:17,370 --> 00:14:19,700
So what?

227
00:14:20,170 --> 00:14:22,470
You are down and out.

228
00:14:23,170 --> 00:14:25,220
What can you do to me?

229
00:14:29,420 --> 00:14:32,610
Well, let’s take good care of

230
00:14:32,610 --> 00:14:34,480
His Excellency’s maid.

231
00:14:36,310 --> 00:14:37,400
Let your maid

232
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:39,390
take off the bandage on her face.

233
00:14:44,820 --> 00:14:46,150
Hurry up!

234
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:51,610
Haven’t you heard
Young Master Yuwen’s order?

235
00:14:54,130 --> 00:14:55,060
Stop!

236
00:14:59,400 --> 00:15:00,220
Princess.

237
00:15:04,030 --> 00:15:04,720
Wei Shuyou.

238
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:06,690
You’re putting on airs.

239
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:09,090
Am I at the Oriole Courtyard?

240
00:15:09,420 --> 00:15:11,300
Or did I come to the wrong place

241
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:13,380
and end up in your family’s backyard?

242
00:15:14,690 --> 00:15:15,460
Princess.

243
00:15:15,880 --> 00:15:18,120
Young Master Wei is acting by the book.

244
00:15:18,260 --> 00:15:19,700
By the book?

245
00:15:20,050 --> 00:15:21,600
What book?

246
00:15:21,760 --> 00:15:23,340
And whose book?

247
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:25,540
My father sent you here

248
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:27,670
to protect Yan Xun

249
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,400
and guard

250
00:15:29,400 --> 00:15:30,240
the Oriole Courtyard.

251
00:15:30,640 --> 00:15:33,350
Meaning you two

252
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,110
are the servants

253
00:15:35,450 --> 00:15:36,750
and Yan Xun

254
00:15:36,750 --> 00:15:37,440
is the master here.

255
00:15:37,810 --> 00:15:39,140
Servants are searching master’s place?

256
00:15:39,620 --> 00:15:41,270
Who do you think you are?

257
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:53,340
Listen carefully,

258
00:15:53,710 --> 00:15:55,260
from now on, the master here

259
00:15:55,260 --> 00:15:56,800
is Yan Xun.

260
00:15:56,800 --> 00:15:58,590
Whoever you work for,

261
00:15:58,790 --> 00:16:00,380
and whatever you’re up to,

262
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:00,960
put them all behind

263
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:02,170
as long as you’re here.

264
00:16:02,850 --> 00:16:04,660
If I find out

265
00:16:04,870 --> 00:16:06,090
you say one thing

266
00:16:06,090 --> 00:16:07,270
and do another,

267
00:16:07,390 --> 00:16:08,190
or even

268
00:16:08,890 --> 00:16:10,900
play tricks,

269
00:16:11,390 --> 00:16:12,430
I am telling you

270
00:16:12,800 --> 00:16:13,780
your masters can’t

271
00:16:13,780 --> 00:16:15,070
protect you.

272
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,400
Get out if you’re clear.

273
00:16:19,540 --> 00:16:20,410
Aye.

274
00:16:32,740 --> 00:16:35,680
Yan Xun, are you all right?

275
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:40,340
I’m fine. Thank you, Your Highness.

276
00:16:41,040 --> 00:16:42,020
Let’s go inside.

277
00:16:42,950 --> 00:16:45,450
Your Highness should be received properly,

278
00:16:45,450 --> 00:16:46,740
but this place

279
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:47,620
is a mess.

280
00:16:47,620 --> 00:16:48,330
Go away!

281
00:16:48,700 --> 00:16:50,100
- I am not here for you.
- Your Highness.

282
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:51,130
Go away!

283
00:16:51,610 --> 00:16:52,600
This place

284
00:16:52,600 --> 00:16:53,960
is too filthy for you to stay.

285
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,130
Are you deaf?

286
00:16:55,130 --> 00:16:56,130
I said, go away.

287
00:16:56,130 --> 00:16:58,520
With all due respect, His Excellency Yan’s family

288
00:16:58,520 --> 00:17:00,060
has been executed.

289
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:01,940
Please don’t be on his side.

290
00:17:03,010 --> 00:17:04,500
Not on his side?

