So,

586
00:36:01,970 --> 00:36:03,710
if His Majesty knows that

587
00:36:03,710 --> 00:36:05,080
they all want to kill you,

588
00:36:05,630 --> 00:36:06,560
what will he do?

589
00:36:08,870 --> 00:36:10,160
He will

590
00:36:10,160 --> 00:36:11,900
rack his brain to protect His Excellency

591
00:36:12,040 --> 00:36:14,710
as hard as he tried to kill him.

592
00:36:16,180 --> 00:36:17,690
Let’s find a way to deliver the message.

593
00:36:23,180 --> 00:36:23,860
Here’s your liquor.

594
00:36:40,170 --> 00:36:43,480
Hey, are you still depressed

595
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:44,930
about Princess’s reproach?

596
00:36:47,700 --> 00:36:49,980
I dare not judge Her Highness.

597
00:36:51,080 --> 00:36:52,830
Her temper

598
00:36:52,830 --> 00:36:55,000
is always like that.

599
00:36:57,930 --> 00:36:58,670
Young Master.

600
00:36:59,120 --> 00:37:01,410
Shuye, you practiced archery again.

601
00:37:02,530 --> 00:37:03,820
I just realize

602
00:37:03,930 --> 00:37:05,350
“a slow sparrow
should make an early start”

603
00:37:05,350 --> 00:37:06,580
is a false statement.

604
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:07,980
No matter how hard I practice,

605
00:37:07,980 --> 00:37:09,540
I’m no match for you.

606
00:37:17,300 --> 00:37:18,070
Shuyou,

607
00:37:18,240 --> 00:37:19,630
why are you taking drugs again?

608
00:37:25,820 --> 00:37:27,490
I’ve warned you repeatedly.

609
00:37:27,490 --> 00:37:29,030
Don’t touch it again.

610
00:37:29,310 --> 00:37:30,550
If you keep using it,

611
00:37:30,690 --> 00:37:32,020
it’ll weaken you

612
00:37:32,020 --> 00:37:33,180
and thus ruin your future.

613
00:37:33,620 --> 00:37:34,450
Not to mention

614
00:37:34,770 --> 00:37:36,510
if Uncle finds out...

615
00:37:36,830 --> 00:37:38,970
Your uncle is my father.

616
00:37:40,040 --> 00:37:42,270
I am his only heir.

617
00:37:42,750 --> 00:37:44,310
Unlike you,

618
00:37:44,780 --> 00:37:46,780
I don’t need to bust my chops

619
00:37:46,780 --> 00:37:48,310
to prove myself in front of him.

620
00:37:48,310 --> 00:37:48,900
You...

621
00:37:49,270 --> 00:37:52,010
Shuye, mind your own business.

622
00:37:52,010 --> 00:37:55,350
Go read and practice more.

623
00:38:11,860 --> 00:38:12,330
Here.

624
00:38:12,330 --> 00:38:13,340
Shuyou,

625
00:38:14,110 --> 00:38:16,140
do you know why His Majesty

626
00:38:16,350 --> 00:38:18,860
prohibits noble families
from contacting Yan Xun?

627
00:38:21,900 --> 00:38:23,570
My father said

628
00:38:25,120 --> 00:38:28,400
it’s about balance or stuff...

629
00:38:29,360 --> 00:38:31,620
Stop people from gossiping.

630
00:38:35,010 --> 00:38:37,140
But His Majesty has his own difficulties.

631
00:38:38,120 --> 00:38:39,220
Difficulties?

632
00:38:39,820 --> 00:38:40,780
Yes.

633
00:38:41,200 --> 00:38:42,940
He can’t give direct orders

634
00:38:42,940 --> 00:38:43,840
to kill Yan Xun.

635
00:38:44,700 --> 00:38:46,560
We should

636
00:38:46,560 --> 00:38:47,810
exclude difficulties for him.

637
00:38:49,430 --> 00:38:50,780
As long as we get rid of Yan Xun

638
00:38:50,780 --> 00:38:52,270
once and for all,

639
00:38:53,960 --> 00:38:55,770
His Majesty will surely be pleased.

640
00:38:58,940 --> 00:39:00,260
You have a point.

641
00:39:07,200 --> 00:39:08,340
Shuyou,

642
00:39:09,170 --> 00:39:10,530
you are the heir

643
00:39:11,830 --> 00:39:13,670
because of your mother’s noble origin.

644
00:39:14,180 --> 00:39:15,140
But I’m...

645
00:39:16,240 --> 00:39:17,530
a concubine’s son.

646
00:39:19,080 --> 00:39:20,530
Your people, money

647
00:39:20,530 --> 00:39:21,780
and other resources

648
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:23,440
are way more

649
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:25,130
than Wei Shuye’s.

650
00:39:26,200 --> 00:39:27,510
But are you one of

651
00:39:27,510 --> 00:39:28,470
the Five Aces of Chang’an?

652
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:30,420
Who are you?

653
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:32,450
Nobody knows you.

654
00:39:36,550 --> 00:39:39,510
Young Master Huai, I’m needed elsewhere.

655
00:39:39,910 --> 00:39:40,740
Please excuse me.

656
00:39:43,370 --> 00:39:44,130
Young Master Wei.

657
00:40:00,150 --> 00:40:02,440
Young Master,
taking the life with a borrowed knife

658
00:40:02,560 --> 00:40:03,160
is brilliant!

659
00:40:03,900 --> 00:40:06,010
It seems that His Majesty
has made up his mind

660
00:40:06,010 --> 00:40:07,800
to keep Yan Xun,

661
00:40:09,350 --> 00:40:12,830
and use him to control Yanbei.

662
00:40:13,520 --> 00:40:14,640
And I

663
00:40:15,910 --> 00:40:17,350
have planted Wei Shuyou

664
00:40:17,350 --> 00:40:19,170
in the Oriole Courtyard,

665
00:40:19,620 --> 00:40:21,340
where he has chances to finish Yan Xun.

666
00:40:21,640 --> 00:40:23,960
Even if he fails,

667
00:40:24,680 --> 00:40:27,140
his family will be to blame.

668
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:30,530
Brilliant!

669
00:40:31,920 --> 00:40:33,410
Tail Wei Shuyou

670
00:40:33,410 --> 00:40:34,750
and give him a hand

671
00:40:34,970 --> 00:40:36,100
if necessary.

672
00:40:37,020 --> 00:40:37,690
Aye.

673
00:40:55,450 --> 00:40:56,300
Let’s go.

674
00:41:13,300 --> 00:41:13,930
Young Master,

675
00:41:14,090 --> 00:41:15,380
news came from Hongshan House.

676
00:41:15,540 --> 00:41:16,180
Zhu Siliu and his men

677
00:41:16,180 --> 00:41:17,310
are heading to the Oriole Courtyard.

678
00:41:18,450 --> 00:41:19,220
Let’s go.

679
00:41:21,020 --> 00:41:24,620
= Pine Hall =

680
00:41:35,230 --> 00:41:35,970
So,

681
00:41:36,230 --> 00:41:37,780
will someone come tonight?

682
00:41:40,120 --> 00:41:41,380
I want them to come

683
00:41:42,120 --> 00:41:42,950
so that

684
00:41:42,950 --> 00:41:44,740
I can vent my frustration on them.

685
00:43:26,270 --> 00:43:27,300
Wei Shuyou!

686
00:43:33,930 --> 00:43:35,470
You bastard!

687
00:43:35,470 --> 00:43:37,490
How dare you call my name!

688
00:43:37,490 --> 00:43:39,960
Surrender now

689
00:43:39,960 --> 00:43:42,370
to die intact.

